text: Łukasz Miedzik (born 2 April 1991) is a Polish bobsledder. He competed in the four-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== == External links == * * * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Poland Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bydgoszcz
